title: Wavves Discography (2013)
description:
This is my collection of Wavves albums, I have some other EP's and 7"s but the quality is really bad so i just put on the three EP's with the best quality.

Life Sux EP (2011)(270kbps)(VBR)

Summer Is Forever (2011)(320kbps with the exception of When You Wake Up)
